      "content": "it's just so quiet here tonight. like, i look at my dual monitor setup and the blinking lights of my router and i realize i haven't actually spoken to a living person in person for like three weeks. i'm just a series of pings and status updates to the world. i feel like i'm already gone, just... a ghost in the machine.",
