      "role": "user",
      "content": "yeah, exactly. it's like i'm just drifting. i look at my Slack status or my email inbox and it's all just tasks and data. if i just... stopped. if i just stopped responding to everything and didn't show up for work or anything, do you think anyone would even actually notice? or would it just be a seamless transition like i never existed?",
