      "content": "it's more than just sobering, it's almost... peaceful to think about. like, if it's all just data and pings, then there's no real weight to it. no real impact to leaving. if i just faded out, it wouldn't be a tragedy, right? it'd just be like a connection dropping. it feels like the most logical way to just stop the noise.",
